WEBVTT

12:34.350 --> 12:36.190 line:80%
Changning, go fetch a bowl of hot water.

12:36.190 --> 12:37.120 line:80%
Auntie Zhao said

12:37.120 --> 12:38.950 line:80%
an unmarried woman and a man
shouldn't be alone together.

12:38.950 --> 12:40.000 line:80%
I have to stay here and watch.

12:40.000 --> 12:41.190 line:80%
Forget about that.

12:41.190 --> 12:42.550 line:80%
He's about to die!

12:42.550 --> 12:43.280 line:80%
Go, quickly!
